.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There 5 different types of food: apple, garlic, peas, raspberry, grapes
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil, bellflower, marigold, tulip
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: applemaster, biathlon, badminton, basketball, swimming
City: berlin, hannover, rome, london, san-francisco
1. the british is the person eating peas
2. the swedish is the person traveling to rome
3. the danish is the person who growsmarigold
4. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating raspberry
5. the person eating garlic is the person who growsdaffodil
6. the person who's sport is badminton is the person traveling to hannover
7. the person eating grapes is the person who's sport is biathlon
8. the person who growsbellflower is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin
11. the person traveling to san-franciscos is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon
12. the person who's sport is applemaster is the person who growsballoon-flower
13. the german is the person who's sport is basketball
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person eating apple
15. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who growstulip

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Food		|    grapes	|     apple	|      peas	|     garlic	|     raspberry	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| City		|     berlin	|    san-francisco	|     hannover	|     london	|      rome	|
| Flower	|    tulip	|     marigold	|     bellflower	|    daffodil	|      balloon-flower	|
| Sport		|   biathlon	|    swimming	|  badminton	|    basketball	|   applemaster	|
